==== core/call_ref.wast ====
Wax type-checking should have failed (type mismatch):
  type t = fn();
  fn f(r: &?func) {
      (r as &?t)();
  }
from wasm:
  (type $t (func))
  (func $f (param $r funcref) (call_ref $t (local.get $r)))
