==== core/gc/br_on_cast.wast ====
Wax type-checking should have failed (type mismatch):
  type t = { };
  fn f(x: &any) -> &?t 'l: {
      do &any {
          br_on_cast 'l &?t x;
      }
      unreachable;
  }
from wasm:
  (type $t (struct))
  (func (param (ref any)) (result (ref null $t))
    (block (result (ref any))
      (br_on_cast 1 (ref any) (ref null $t) (local.get 0)))
    (unreachable)
  )
Wax type-checking should have failed (type mismatch):
  fn f() -> &?any 'l: {
      unreachable;
      br_on_cast 'l &?any _;
  }
from wasm: (func (result anyref) (br_on_cast 0 eqref anyref (unreachable)))
Wax type-checking should have failed (type mismatch):
  fn f() -> &?any 'l: {
      unreachable;
      br_on_cast 'l &?array _;
  }
from wasm:
  (func (result anyref) (br_on_cast 0 structref arrayref (unreachable)))
==== core/gc/br_on_cast_fail.wast ====
Wax type-checking should have failed (type mismatch):
  type t = { };
  fn f(x: &any) -> &any 'l: {
      (do &?t {
           br_on_cast_fail 'l &?t x;
       }!);
  }
from wasm:
  (type $t (struct))
  (func (param (ref any)) (result (ref any))
    (block (result (ref null $t))
      (br_on_cast_fail 1 (ref any) (ref null $t) (local.get 0)))
    (ref.as_non_null)
  )
